  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5273508/" class="title-link">语言、左右脑与人的分裂</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5273508"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/foxtrotofzephyr/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3770209-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/foxtrotofzephyr/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">padma</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-01-18"
      class="main-meta">2012-01-18 12:36:30</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5273508_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  书中提到，语言的创造直至被书写，最终标志了人的左右脑分离。而在左右脑还互相联结的状态，人是更加完整且接近神性的。某个北美印第安部落至今拒绝书写他们的语言，认为那是亵渎神的，是危险的。忽然想到淮南子中写到仓颉造字也用了一段令人恐惧的文字：天雨粟，鬼夜哭。

